creator: Teach on Mars
descriptionHtml:
Teach on Mars, the coolest way to learn in the galaxy.

Improve your skills every day with hundreds of fun and varied learning activities, accessible on- and off-line. Customize your profile and your preferences. Challenge your friends and colleagues. Collect badges and score points to reach the top of the leaderboard. Stay up to date with the news feed. Earn certificates and become an expert.

Do you want to use this application to train your learners? Are you a company or a training organization? Create engaging, multilingual training content using our simple and powerful authoring tool, then test and publish it with just one click. Manage your learners, analyse learning statistics, interface with your software ecosystem (LMS, CRM, etc.), and even customize the application with your branding. Visit www.teachonmars.com for more information.
